item.title: Module Catalog Page
item.description: SPECIFICATIONS - MODULE CATALOG > MODULE CATALOG PAGE [TO BE COMPLETED] Modules header Upload a module. [TO BE COMPLETED] If the module zip file is too big, the upload fails and the modal window notices the error: Clicking on ‘What happened?’ should display Your uploaded file might exceed the upload_max_filesize and the post_max_size directives in php.ini, please check your server configuration. in Admin.Notifications.Error, cf. to do #16428 issue.
